== 與人類的關係 ==
[[File:Yellow_mite_(Tydeidae)_Lorryia_formosa_2_edit.jpg|thumb]]。]]
以往[[美國原住民|美國原住民]]是會吃[[鱟|鱟]]，用其尾棘製作矛頭，殼用來舀水。不過他們已經放棄了將鱟作為牲畜食物，因為發現會令牲畜肉質的味道變壞。鱟的[[血液|血液]]含有[[鱟阿米巴樣細胞溶解物|鱟阿米巴樣細胞溶解物]]（Limulus Amebocyte Lysate）可以用作[[細菌|細菌]]存在的試劑，以及用來偵測[[腦膜炎|腦膜炎]]及一些[[癌症|癌症]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Coast|author=Heard, W.|url=http://www.marine.usf.edu/pjocean/packets/f01/f01u5p3.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-08-25|publisher=University of South Florida|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219095700/http://www.marine.usf.edu/pjocean/packets/f01/f01u5p3.pdf|archive-date=2017-02-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

在[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]<ref>{{cite book|author=Ray, N.|year=2002|title=Lonely Planet Cambodia|publisher=LonelyPlanet Publications|isbn=1-74059-111-9|page=308}}</ref>及[[委內瑞拉|委內瑞拉]]南部<ref>{{cite book|author=Weil, C.|title=Fierce Food|year=2006|publisher=Plume|isbn=0452287006|url=http://www.budgettravel.com/bt-dyn/content/article/2006/10/24/AR2006102400797.html|accessdate=2008-10-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511192407/http://www.budgettravel.com/bt-dyn/content/article/2006/10/24/AR2006102400797.html|archivedate=2011-05-11}}</ref>會煮食[[捕鳥蛛科|捕鳥蛛科]]，並視為是一種美食。蜘蛛[[毒素|毒素]]對環境的污染較傳統的[[殺蟲劑|殺蟲劑]]為低，因只會對[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]（而不是[[脊椎動物|脊椎動物]]）起作用。<ref>{{cite web|title=Spider Venom Could Yield Eco-Friendly Insecticides|publisher=National Science Foundation (USA)|url=http://www.nsf.gov/discoveries/disc_summ.jsp?cntn_id=100676&org=NSF|accessdate=2008-10-11|archive-date=2012-06-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/687ngjeEj?url=http://www.nsf.gov/discoveries/disc_summ.jsp?cntn_id=100676|dead-url=no}}</ref>蜘蛛毒素也正研究用作醫藥來治療[[心律不整|心律不整]]<ref>{{cite journal|author=Novak, K.|title=Spider venom helps hearts keep their rhythm|journal=Nature Medicine|volume=7|issue=155|year=2001|pmid=11175840|doi=10.1038/84588|pages=155}}</ref>、[[阿茲海默病|阿茲海默病]]<ref>{{cite journal|author=Lewis, R.J., and Garcia, M.L.|title=Therapeutic potential of venom peptides|journal=Nature Reviews Drug Discovery|volume=2|issue=10|pages=790–802|date=October 2003|pmid=14526382|doi=10.1038/nrd1197|url=http://imb.uq.edu.au/download/large/Venom_therapeutics.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-10-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216214632/http://imb.uq.edu.au/download/large/Venom_therapeutics.pdf|archivedate=2008-12-16}}</ref>、[[中風|中風]]<ref>{{cite journal|author=Bogin, O.|title=Venom Peptides and their Mimetics as Potential Drugs|journal=Modulator|issue=19|date=Spring 2005|url=http://www.alomone.com/System/UpLoadFiles/DGallery/Docs/Venom%20Peptides%20and%20their%20Mimetics%20as%20Potential%20Drugs.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-10-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081209094652/http://www.alomone.com/System/UpLoadFiles/DGallery/Docs/Venom%20Peptides%20and%20their%20Mimetics%20as%20Potential%20Drugs.pdf|archivedate=2008-12-09}}</ref>及[[勃起功能障礙|勃起功能障礙]]。<ref>{{cite journal|date=June 2008|author=Andrade, E., Villanova, F., Borra, P., ''et al.''|title=Penile erection induced ''in vivo'' by a purified toxin from the Brazilian spider ''Phoneutria nigriventer''|journal=British Journal of Urology International|volume=102|issue=7| pages=835–7|doi=10.1111/j.1464-410X.2008.07762.x|pmid=18537953|year=2008}}</ref>由於蜘蛛絲輕巧而堅韌，[[基因工程師|基因工程師]]嘗試利用羊奶及[[葉子|葉子]]來製作蜘蛛絲。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Hinman, M.B., Jones J.A., and Lewis, R.W.|title=Synthetic spider silk: a modular fiber|journal=Trends in Biotechnology|volume=18|issue=9|date=September 2000|pmid=10942961|pages=374–9|doi=10.1016/S0167-7799(00)01481-5|url=http://www.tech.plym.ac.uk/sme/FailureCases/Natural_Structures/Synthetic_spider_silk.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-10-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216214633/http://www.tech.plym.ac.uk/sme/FailureCases/Natural_Structures/Synthetic_spider_silk.pdf|archivedate=2008-12-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Menassa, R., Zhu, H., Karatzas, C.N., Lazaris, A., Richman, A., and Brandle, J.|title=Spider dragline silk proteins in transgenic tobacco leaves: accumulation and field production|journal=Plant Biotechnology Journal|volume=2|issue=5|pages=431–8|date=June 2004|pmid=17168889|doi=10.1111/j.1467-7652.2004.00087.x}}</ref>於20世紀就有約100宗被蜘蛛咬死的個案<ref>{{cite journal|author=Diaz, J.H.|title=The Global Epidemiology, Syndromic Classification, Management, and Prevention of Spider Bites|journal=American Journal of Tropical Medicine and Hygiene|volume=71|issue=2|date=August 1, 2004|pages=239–50|url=http://www.ajtmh.org/cgi/content/abstract/71/2/239|accessdate=2008-10-11|pmid=15306718|archive-date=2011-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511020113/http://www.ajtmh.org/cgi/content/abstract/71/2/239|dead-url=no}}</ref>，相對於[[水母|水母]]刺死的1500宗為小。<ref name="WilliamsonFennerEtAl1996">{{cite book|author=Williamson, J.A., Fenner, P.J., Burnett, J.W., and Rifkin, J.|title=Venomous and Poisonous Marine Animals: A Medical and Biological Handbook|publisher=UNSW Press|year=1996|isbn=0868402796|pages=65–8|url=http://books.google.com/?id=YsZ3GryFIzEC&pg=PA75&lpg=PA75&dq=mollusc+venom+fatal|accessdate=2008-10-03}}</ref>

[[蠍子|蠍子]]刺螯亦是相當危險的，例如在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]每年就約有1000宗死亡個案，但在發展較先進的[[美國|美國]]每年就只有1宗。大部份個案都是因[[人類|人類]]誤闖蠍子巢穴而發生的。<ref>{{cite web|title=Scorpion Sting|author=Cheng, D., Dattaro, J.A., and Yakobi, R.|publisher=WebMD|url=http://www.emedicine.com/med/topic2081.htm|accessdate=2008-10-25|archive-date=2008-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206004945/http://www.emedicine.com/MED/topic2081.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>蠍子毒素也正被開發來作為醫藥用途，包括治療[[腦癌|腦癌]]及[[骨骼|骨骼]]病症。<ref>{{cite web|title='Scorpion venom' attacks tumours|publisher=BBC News|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5214784.stm|accessdate=2008-10-25|date=2006-07-30|archive-date=2019-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814222454/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5214784.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Scorpion venom blocks bone loss|publisher=Harvard University|url=http://harvardscience.harvard.edu/medicine-health/articles/scorpion-venom-blocks-bone-loss|accessdate=2008-10-25|archive-date=2010-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620051306/http://www.harvardscience.harvard.edu/medicine-health/articles/scorpion-venom-blocks-bone-loss|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[蜱|蜱]]是[[寄生|寄生]]的，一些會傳播引發疾病的微生物及[[寄生蟲|寄生蟲]]，一些的口水更會直接引起[[蜱癱瘓|蜱癱瘓]]。<ref>{{Cite book|last1=Goodman|first1=Jesse L.|last2=Dennis|first2=David Tappen|last3=Sonenshine|first3=Daniel E.|title=Tick-borne diseases of humans|url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=dKlUARLKT9IC|accessdate=2010-03-29|year=2005|publisher=ASM Press|isbn=9781555812386|pages=114-401|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026063805/http://books.google.co.in/books?id=dKlUARLKT9IC|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一些[[蟎|蟎]]也會侵擾[[人類|人類]]，它們咬或鑽入[[皮膚|皮膚]]下而引起痕癢。那些侵擾[[齧齒目|齧齒目]]等[[動物|動物]]的[[物種|物種]]在失去主體時也會影響人類。<ref>{{cite web|title=Parasitic Mites of Humans|author=Potter, M.F.|publisher=University of Kentucky College of Agriculture|url=http://www.ca.uky.edu/entomology/entfacts/ef637.asp|accessdate=2008-10-25|archive-date=2009-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108202742/http://www.ca.uky.edu/entomology/entfacts/ef637.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>有三種蟎會對[[蜜蜂|蜜蜂]]造成危害，其中一種的[[瓦蟎|瓦蟎]]是[[養蜂人|養蜂人]]的勁敵。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Jong, D.D., Morse, R.A., and Eickwort, G.C.|title=Mite Pests of Honey Bees|journal=Annual Review of Entomology|volume=27|pages=229–52|date=January 1982|doi=10.1146/annurev.en.27.010182.001305}}</ref>蟎會引起多種過敏症，包括[[過敏性鼻炎|過敏性鼻炎]]、[[哮喘|哮喘]]及[[濕疹|濕疹]]，與及加劇[[異位性皮膚炎|異位性皮膚炎]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.netdoctor.co.uk/health_advice/facts/allergyhousedustmite.htm|title=House dust mite allergy|publisher=NetDoctor|author=Klenerman, Paul; Lipworth, Brian; authors|accessdate=2008-02-20|archive-date=2008-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080211110450/http://www.netdoctor.co.uk/health_advice/facts/allergyhousedustmite.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>它們也是[[害蟲|害蟲]]，但掠食性的蟎可以控制它們。<ref name="Shultz2001"/><ref>{{cite journal|author=Osakabe, M.|title=Which predatory mite can control both a dominant mite pest, ''Tetranychus urticae'', and a latent mite pest, ''Eotetranychus asiaticus'', on strawberry?|journal=Experimental & applied acarology|year=2002|volume=26|issue=3-4|pages=219–30|doi=10.1023/A:1021116121604}}</ref>
